{"tid":333731,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求你地啲肥婆唔好再出街","createTime":"2017-07-24T05:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T06:19:29.000Z","uid":8078,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4be22847163dba3037f7d19a6609dbf1f4f795","tid":333731,"uid":8078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母呀死肥婆</span></span><br />\n大熱天時就留返係屋企涼你既冷氣啦<br />\n出乜撚野街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n次次遇著啲肥婆都阻撚住哂<br />\n係商場啲開門位就變身廢老一樣<br />\n企定係度等人開門<br />\n屌你阻撚住我都唔講<br />\n我走去開門都盡量開大啲驚你成舊隕石咁入唔到<br />\n點知都係唔撚夠大入唔到 最後你咪又係要自己出手開門<br />\n然後仲要睥撚住我好似我唔啱咁<br />\n<br />\n跟住搭地鐵嗰陣例牌會有啲肥婆同你爭落車<br />\n我同你都係下一個站落 我都企撚左係個門口度準備落<br />\n啲肥婆最鍾意就係度推推撞撞唔該借借驚死落唔到咁<br />\n你講借借唔緊要呀 你推撚埋我落對門度呀<br />\n當你自己係咩呀 破冰船呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心肥婆唔應該出街<br />\n你地知唔知你地搞到其他人出街好似跑緊障礙賽咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffa98b4e6fb268b04efa3805525a40fa8c857fb","tid":333731,"uid":73051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"見到都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dd401d59c7982b158f1faba6c4d17d3ccada4a","tid":333731,"uid":15114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"662410a580a4ec70c5d9a0fc52e934ce03239234","tid":333731,"uid":8078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲仲要以為自己model咁化行妝<br />\n跟住行幾步路就出哂汗個妝都溶左一半<br />\n見到就想一野嘔落佢地塊面度<br />\n<br />\nbtw hyeri<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1aa318ef01d895ab9c081ee70953f9ab27c29a","ti